Day 10: SQL – Subqueries & Views

Topic:
SQL Subqueries and Views

Learning Objectives:

Understand nested and correlated subqueries
Learn how subqueries are used inside SELECT, WHERE, and FROM clauses
Understand the purpose and advantages of SQL Views
Learn how to create, use, and remove views in a database
Explore real-world use cases for reusable query views

Activities / Deliverables:

Rewrite 3 existing JOIN queries as subqueries
Practice nested and correlated subquery examples
Create 3 reusable views in VolyoDB
Test and verify outputs from created views
Use CREATE VIEW and DROP VIEW commands for view management

Tools / Tech:

MySQL 8

